com.ziluck.factions.spatial

Class BoundedArea

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ziluck.factions.spatial.BoundedArea
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.github.davidmoten.rtree.geometry.Geometry, com.github.davidmoten.rtree.geometry.HasGeometry, com.github.davidmoten.rtree.geometry.Rectangle
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Claim2D

    public class BoundedArea
extends Object
implements com.github.davidmoten.rtree.geometry.Rectangle
    Represents a two-dimensional bounded area.

    BoundedArea also implements the R-Tree interface Rectangle. This allows spatial and geometric operations to be performed on it with ease.

    Author:
    Michael Ziluck
